Here is an Aeonic orb for epic of my own design. I remixed a few things into this model but a lot is my own or changed heavily. Feel free to adjust scale to size it how you want it. It is currently hollowed and has a hole in the bottom for a flying stand. Enjoy!

EDIT: An upscaled and pieced out version has been added. The complete model will print in one piece on a photon, the upscaled version will require at least 2 prints, 1 for the orb and one for the armor panels. It is much larger, about 75mm at it widest part. I recommend hollowing and adding holes as necessary for cleaning and drainage. Be sure to place interior supports.
